General.Name: Aetherium Acquisition Corp
General.Description: Aetherium Acquisition Corp. focuses on effecting a merger, capital stock exchange, asset acquisition, stock purchase, reorganization, or similar business combination with one or more businesses. It intends to focus on businesses in the education, training, and education technology industries primarily in Asia. Aetherium Acquisition Corp. was incorporated in 2021 and is based in Greenwich, Connecticut.
